# HEL-002: Dockerfile-specific ignore (BuildKit/podman `<Dockerfile>.dockerignore`).
# Allowlist style: the repo-root build context sends ONLY what the build needs.
# On engines without per-Dockerfile ignore support this file is inert and the
# build still succeeds (fail-safe; proven by the recorded green build).
*
!services/notification-service
!submodules/herald
services/notification-service/Dockerfile.dockerignore
submodules/herald/.git
